Package com.example.aurora.models

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.aurora.models.Event
Direct Known Subclasses:
EntrantFeaturesTest.TestableEvent, OrganizerFeaturesTest.TestableEvent
public class Event extends Object
Unified Event model that: - Works with old docs (name, date, capacity, etc.) without crashing. - Works with new docs (title, startDate/endDate, maxSpots, geoRequired, etc.). NOTE: We intentionally DO NOT have any field or getter/setter called "capacity" so Firestore won't try to map the legacy "capacity" field and crash.
